file.name: verify_code.yml
file.content:
Step 2) Return password resetting token if user entered correct 8 digit code
---
openapi: 3.0.0
consumes:
  "application/json"
tags:
  - name: "Forget Password"
parameters:
  - name: body
    in: body
    required: true
    schema:
      required:
        - hashed_data
        - user_input
      properties:
        hashed_data:
          type: string
          description: "Hashed data which is obtained from previous call to /forget_password"
          example: "eyJhb..."
        user_input:
          type: string
          description: "User inputed 8 digit code"
          example: "86119547"
responses:
  200:
    description: "Return token for resetting password if user inputed correct code"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        reset_password_token:
          type: string
          description: "Token for resetting user's password"
      example:
        reset_password_token: "eyJhb..."
  400:
    description: "User inputed code is incorrect"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "User inputed code is incorrect"
      example:
        msg: "User inputed code is incorrect"
  401:
    description: "Token expired!"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "Token expired!"
      example:
        msg: "Token expired!"
  401:
    description: "Token invalid!"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "Token invalid!"
      example:
        msg: "Token invalid!"
